555
00:48:48,124 --> 00:48:49,896
Fé.

556
00:48:49,897 --> 00:48:51,869
Fé e superstição.

557
00:48:52,556 --> 00:48:54,017
No meu primeiro dia aqui,

558
00:48:54,018 --> 00:48:57,290
